ğŸ  St. Denis Police â€‹

Documentation relating to the spooni_sd_police.

DISCLAIMER: This MLO is only an add-on to the existing St. Denis Police MLO from R*

Buy NowView on Map

1. Installation â€‹

spooni_sd_police works Standalone.

To install spooni_sd_police:

  • Download the resource
    • On Cfx.re Portal
  • Drag and drop the resource into your resources folder
    • spooni_sd_police
  • Add this ensure in your server.cfg
      ensure spooni_sd_police
  • At the end, restart the server

If you have any problems, you can always open a ticket in the Spooni Discord.
